<paragraph role="paragraph" id="par_id3159158" xml-lang="en-US" l10n="CHG" oldref="4">To remove the variable watch, select the variable in the Watch window, and then click on the <emph>Enable Watch</emph> icon.</paragraph>
<bookmark xml-lang="en-US" branch="hid/HID_BASICIDE_REMOVEWATCH" id="bm_id3154142" localize="false"/>
<paragraph role="paragraph" id="par_id3152350" xml-lang="en-US" l10n="U" oldref="5"><ahelp hid="HID_BASICIDE_REMOVEWATCH" visibility="hidden">Removes the watch for a selected variable.</ahelp></paragraph>
